OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed in Switzerland for exploiting
OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FFour members of Britain's richest
OL,8,Ffamily have been handed prison
OL,9,Fsentences in Switzerland for
OL,10,Fexploiting servants working in their
OL,11,Fluxury villa.
OL,13,FPrakash Hinduja and his wife, Kamal,
OL,14,Fwere jailed for four and a half years
OL,15,Feach, while their son, Ajay, and his
OL,16,Fwife, Namrata, both received four
OL,17,Fyears in prison.
