OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed in Switzerland for exploiting
OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FThey banned the workers, mostly
OL,8,Filliterate and from India, from
OL,9,Fleaving the villa and forced them to
OL,10,Fwork excruciatingly long days,
OL,11,Fsometimes up to 18 hours.
OL,13,FThe court found the four guilty of
OL,14,Fexploiting the workers, paying them
OL,15,Fwages less than a tenth of the income
OL,16,Ffor domestic work in Switzerland.
OL,18,FThe Hindujas were not found guilty of
OL,19,Fcharges of trafficking, on the grounds
OL,20,Fthe staff in part understood what they
OL,21,Fwere getting into.
