OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed in Switzerland for exploiting
OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FThe family topped this year's Sunday
OL,8,FTimes Rich List of the United
OL,9,FKingdom's wealthiest people, with a
OL,10,Fnet worth of around #37.2 billion.
OL,12,FThey did not attend court, but a fifth
OL,13,Fdefendent - the family's business
OL,14,Fmanager Najib Ziazi - was present, and
OL,15,Freceived an 18-month suspended
OL,16,Fsentence.
OL,18,FEmployees slept in the basement of the
OL,19,Fvilla, in the Cologny neighbourhood of
OL,20,FGeneva, and said Kamal Hinduja
OL,21,Finstilled a "climate of fear".
