OL,5,Cservants
OL,7,FThey also had their passports seized
OL,8,Fand were paid with rupees into banks
OL,9,Fback home that they could not access.
OL,11,FThe Hindujas moved to Switzerland in
OL,12,Fthe late 1980s. Prakash Hinduja was
OL,13,Fconvicted on less serious but similar
OL,14,Fcharges in 2007.
OL,16,FAlong with three of of his brothers,
OL,17,FPrakash Hinduja is a leader of an
OL,18,Findustrial conglomerate in sectors
OL,19,Fincluding information technology,
OL,20,Fmedia, power, real estate and
OL,21,Fhealthcare.
